* Let's get set up!

- https://golang.org/dl (download Go)
- mkdir ~/go/src ~/go/bin ~/go/pkg
- Open or create ~/.bash_profile and add the following two lines: 
    export GOPATH="$HOME/go"
    export PATH="$PATH:$GOPATH/bin"
- Install the Go plugin for your editor. 
- Let's write hello world!


